title: Tracey Carnazzo: Trashy or Italian?
description: The super funny, SUPER Italian Tracey Carnazzo joins us this week. Tracey tells us about being Italian and growing up in NYC, the difference between sauce and gravy, and  how to cut family members out of your life.  You may know Tracey Carnazzo from her podcasts 90 Day Fiance Trash Talk, Teen Mom Trash Talk, and Only in New York. Have Garbage Questions: AreYouGarbage@gmail.com Subscribe. Rate. Review
